sequenceDiagram
    participant T as Sync Trigger
    participant SyncW as SyncUpstreamSourceWorkflow
    participant MSM as MSM API
    participant SS as SimpleStream Source

    T->>SyncW: start workflow (boot_source_id)
    
    SyncW->>+MSM: GET boot source config<br/>(GET_BOOT_SOURCE_ACTIVITY)
    MSM-->>-SyncW: source config + selections
    
    SyncW->>+SS: Fetch SimpleStream index<br/>(FETCH_SS_INDEXES)
    SS-->>-SyncW: product index URLs[]
    
    loop for each product index
        SyncW->>+SS: Load product map<br/>(LOAD_PRODUCT_MAP_ACTIVITY)
        note over SS: fetch product index<br/>check signatures if needed<br/>filter by selections
        SS-->>-SyncW: asset items[]
    end
    
    SyncW->>+MSM: PUT new assets<br/>(PUT_NEW_ASSETS_ACTIVITY)
    note over MSM: create/update assets<br/>determine what needs downloading
    MSM-->>-SyncW: to_download[] (item IDs)
    
    par for each item to download
        SyncW->>SyncW: start DownloadUpstreamImageWorkflow<br/>(ABANDON policy)
    end
    
    SyncW->>SyncW: start RemoveStaleImagesWorkflow<br/>(ABANDON policy)
    note over SyncW: parent doesn't wait<br/>for child to complete
    
    SyncW-->>T: done
